The owner of a farm informed the Midvaal fire department of the crash after hearing a loud explosion. JOHANNESBURG A man has burnt to death after his micro-light aircraft crashed on a Suikerbosrand farm in Meyerton in the Midvaal.The owner of a farm informed the Midvaal fire department of the crash after hearing a loud explosion in the early hours of this morning.The cause of the incident is not yet known.ER24 spokesperson Annine Dormehl said, Paramedics found the pilot burnt to death. 